{"tid":1633561,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"希望大家唔好再召喚神獸","createTime":"2019-10-07T04:27:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T04:43:57.000Z","uid":124247,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ee24ec234a67d6c839d1836250ba92d8853c2104","tid":1633561,"uid":124247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:27:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">改為召喚Batman<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">眾所周知Batman係私了既表表者<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />鑒於曾經有po講過勇武唔太想叫私了，而想叫替天行道，警惡懲奸等等，同時發現私了一事令大家有唔少爭吵<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />小妹諗左好耐，不如試下改下叫法，幫件事加分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">優點:</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">1.形象正面影射:Batman=正義既化身，警惡懲奸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係人都知，有助大眾(特別係中年同路人及淺黃)明白我地係懲罰緊d壞人，只唔係普通巿民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span> <span style=\"font-size: medium;\">亦都唔洗次次私了都解釋到口臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">2.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />形象吻合:Batman=黑衣+蒙面=示威者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3.有助外媒報導:</span></span><span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">鶳了黎講係玩廣東話食字，改用Batman唔係食字，而係食佢既象徵意義，外媒易寫，國際更明我地做緊咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有助文宣:</span></span><span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">相信大家都冇乜係連儂見過私了既文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因爲私了既感覺係有兩方私㡳下搞掂件事既意思，冇高低對錯之說，相反用左batman之後相信要整文宣比大眾消化就易得多了！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">繼續用鶳既憂慮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1.神獸，獅 有猛獸既意思，令人聯想到凶殘同暴力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">勇武曾經提及唔想大家再叫私了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">叫召喚batman真係百利而無一害<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，雖然核爆都唔割，</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但令人明白我地做緊咩係好重要的，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有如最近係直播加旁白師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />改一少步，進一大步呀各位手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FhduO2m.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFhduO2m.png&h=4511a167&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一齊跟我講一次，</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">召喚Batman<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"8b67864b762e81189ffda816bbf97e342ccbf48f","tid":1633561,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:27:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">又話杯葛？<br />\n又話抗爭？<br />\n繼續俾錢佢賺去出賣港人？<br />\n和理非平時返工唔好再俾正價搭黨鐵！<br />\n無得揀嘅情況例外</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/237n0J0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F237n0J0.jpg&h=61248f49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o0TeRHg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo0TeRHg.jpg&h=94f567e9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RFtRTVB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRFtRTVB.jpg&h=5322f0ae&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vxJ20AB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvxJ20AB.jpg&h=c7141e62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JFpQ9Cb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJFpQ9Cb.jpg&h=a7156522&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">如果和理非連咁小野都做唔到<br />\n就唔好學人話抗爭</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rHxjrJf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrHxjrJf.jpg&h=8688cd40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">聽日<span style=\"color: red;\">全民三罷</span>！！！<br />\n當十幾歲嘅學生中槍，<br />\n咁多個人冇咗隻眼，<br />\n咁多個義士死諫，<br />\n仲可以正常返工返學？</span>"},{"pid":"20b09a24323fe4bae22e033217310eab7404633e","tid":1633561,"uid":124247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:31:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">召喚batman</span></span>"},{"pid":"a2df0c5ec1422653524bdeff465ddde12e64b85c","tid":1633561,"uid":124247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:35:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">召喚Batmbn<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"59fdb59ddb02fc74c943880a5a8312750ff9fe5a","tid":1633561,"uid":124247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:35:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">召喚Batman<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"d082179dcca6545411e801c3d8382572360a1a73","tid":1633561,"uid":124247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:36:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">召喚Batman<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"d1abab3b1079b2cf8b7d6c568181e5c3a476fc49","tid":1633561,"uid":124247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:37:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">召喚Batman<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"cae2d1558f350c64afb83a90aa268a69eccf7707","tid":1633561,"uid":124247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:37:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">召喚Batman<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"8dc075772c550732f1dedf629e510ca558f0ba08","tid":1633561,"uid":124247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:38:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">召喚Batman<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"1d501f02cc98bfbe659901d2e01d48f35b6ec5c8","tid":1633561,"uid":124247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:39:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">召喚Batman<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"2abd15ce8a0c587b4a2a06c7d32461fa56270783","tid":1633561,"uid":124247,